"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427635","Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","false","2015-11-19","<p>The average water and sewerage bill in the St Helens North constituency and Merseyside was £359 in 2010 and £411 in 2015. Both of these areas are served by United Utilities. The average water and sewerage bill in England and Wales was £339 in 2010 and £385 in 2015.</p>","Penrith and The Border","Rory Stewart",,"2015-11-19T09:31:00.537Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427635/answer","Biography information for Rory Stewart","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427635/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427635/answer",,,,,"13","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","2015-11-10","Water Charges","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs, what the average household bill for water was in (a) St Helens North constituency, (b) Merseyside and (c) the UK in (i) 2010 and (ii) 2015.","false","Biography information for Conor McGinn","St Helens North","Conor McGinn","16048"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427636","Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","false","2015-11-17","<p>The Government is focused on delivering a successful renegotiation. We believe we can and will succeed in reforming and renegotiating our relationship with the EU and campaigning to keep the UK in the EU on that basis.</p>","Camborne and Redruth","George Eustice",,"2015-11-17T16:15:12.817Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427636/answer","Biography information for George Eustice","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427636/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/427636/answer",,,,,"13","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","Environment, Food and Rural Affairs","2015-11-10","Agriculture: Northern Ireland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs, what preparations her Department is making to support the agricultural economy in the Northern Ireland in the event of the UK leaving the EU.","false","Biography information for Dr Alasdair McDonnell","Belfast South","Dr Alasdair McDonnell","15824"
